323
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:21,400
Kto? Muž? Je to muž?

324
00:29:21,930 --> 00:29:24,640
Myslíte? Je to muž?

325
00:29:24,660 --> 00:29:26,280
Ach... kretén.

326
